    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the elements of <strong>Fractala Sandbox</strong> and its large-scale physics-based simulation. A pure sandbox experience featuring everything from wavy water and sticky slime to viscous lava, coiling honey, squishy jelly, compressible snow, piling sand, aerodynamics, solids, rope, fire, and explosives!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/e13bf12d7c0e30e373848675a41348a7.poster.avif?t=1755291233\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/e13bf12d7c0e30e373848675a41348a7.webm?t=1755291233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/e13bf12d7c0e30e373848675a41348a7.mp4?t=1755291233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sandbox aims to spark player creativity through its highly interconnected simulation, leveraging the graphics card to simulate vast quantities of particles in real-time. Experiment with different materials, discover unforeseen reactions, and use your findings in a larger contraption. Or tinker with items and combine them to make a pretty diorama.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some order, lots of chaos, and a fractal to be found in between.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/236466454ade0101b7c5fb889361954b.poster.avif?t=1755291233\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/236466454ade0101b7c5fb889361954b.webm?t=1755291233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/236466454ade0101b7c5fb889361954b.mp4?t=1755291233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to get into the nitty-gritty, use the item editor to create your own specialized items to fit the needs of your current creation. With modding tools, you can add new behaviors and material reactions to the base game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/f3bc6ecde9c7a40f77c0174fd08e5ce8.poster.avif?t=1755291233\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/f3bc6ecde9c7a40f77c0174fd08e5ce8.webm?t=1755291233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/f3bc6ecde9c7a40f77c0174fd08e5ce8.mp4?t=1755291233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And don't forget to share your findings and creations with the rest of the community!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/16a947336bcccb657f8f0ffb9a9236f6.poster.avif?t=1755291233\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/16a947336bcccb657f8f0ffb9a9236f6.webm?t=1755291233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289350/extras/16a947336bcccb657f8f0ffb9a9236f6.mp4?t=1755291233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fractalier's endeavor, as infinite as the patterns they study.</p>",
